### Key Logical Groupings:
1. 1.
   Academic Management - Students, Teachers, Classes, Exams
2. 2.
   Financial Management - Budgets, Fees, Salaries, Purchases
3. 3.
   Inventory Management - Assets, Maintenance, Depreciation
4. 4.
   Security & Auditing - Authentication, Authorization, Logging
5. 5.
   API & Integration - RESTful APIs, External Services
6. 6.
   Reporting & Analytics - Comprehensive reporting system
7. 7.
   Backup & Recovery - Automated backup and restore
8. 8.
   Testing & Quality - Comprehensive test suite